'''贝兹细胞'''（英文：Betz cell），又称'''贝茨锥体细胞'''（pyramidal cells of Betz），是指[[初级运动皮层|初级运动皮层]]第5层[[灰质|灰质]]中的巨型[[锥体细胞|锥体细胞]]（[[神经元|神经元]]）<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Betz Cell - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/betz-cell|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Betz cells {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/betz-cells?lang=us#:~:text=Betz%20cells%20are%20pyramidal%20cell,cells%20of%20the%20spinal%20cord.|accessdate=2021-03-06|last=Gaillard|first=Frank|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419212209/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/betz-cells?lang=us#:~:text=Betz%20cells%20are%20pyramidal%20cell,cells%20of%20the%20spinal%20cord.|dead-url=no}}</ref>。贝兹细胞是[[中枢神经系统|中枢神经系统]]中最大的神经元，直径可达100[[微米|微米]]<ref>{{Cite book|chapter=|url=http://archive.org/details/neuroscienceissu00purv|publisher=Sunderland, Mass. : Sinauer|date=2008|isbn=978-0-87893-697-7|last=Purves|first=Dale|title=Neuroscience}}</ref><ref name="Nolte_2002">Nolte, J. ''The Human Brain'', 5th ed. Mosby: Missouri; 2002, p.527. {{ISBN|0-323-01320-1}}</ref>。该细胞以[[俄罗斯帝国|俄国]]（现[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]地区）科学家{{le|弗拉基米尔·贝兹|Vladimir Betz}}的名字命名<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The discovery of the pyramidal neurons: Vladimir Betz and a new era of neuroscience|url=https://academic.oup.com/brain/article/135/1/285/324598|last=Kushchayev|first=Sergiy V.|last2=Moskalenko|first2=Vitaliy F.|date=2012-01-01|journal=Brain|issue=1|doi=10.1093/brain/awr276|volume=135|pages=285–300|language=en|issn=0006-8950|last3=Wiener|first3=Philip C.|last4=Tsymbaliuk|first4=Vitaliy I.|last5=Cherkasov|first5=Viktor G.|last6=Dzyavulska|first6=Irina V.|last7=Kovalchuk|first7=Oleksander I.|last8=Sonntag|first8=Volker K. H.|last9=Spetzler|first9=Robert F.|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211230730/https://academic.oup.com/brain/article/135/1/285/324598|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

贝兹细胞属于{{le|上部运动神经元|Upper motor neuron}}，其长[[轴突|轴突]]通过[[皮質脊髓束|皮质脊髓束]]进入[[脊髓|脊髓]]<ref name=":0" />。在人体中，贝兹细胞的神经纤维通过[[突触|突触]]与{{le|前灰柱|Anterior grey column}}细胞相连，后者另一端连接着[[肌肉|肌肉]]。贝兹细胞拥有一般锥体细胞上常见的顶端[[树突|树突]]（apical dendrite），此外他们还拥有更多的初级树突分支，几乎可从[[细胞体|细胞体]]的各个部位延伸出<ref name="Braak_Braak_1976">{{cite journal|title=The pyramidal cells of Betz within the cingulate and precentral gigantopyramidal field in the human brain. A Golgi and pigmentarchitectonic study.|first1=H|last2=Braak|first2=E|journal=Cell and Tissue Research|issue=1|doi=10.1007/bf00226052|year=1976|volume=172|pages=103–19|pmid=991201|last1=Braak}}</ref>。这些周围树突和{{le|基底树突|Basal dendrite}}可延伸至皮层各层，但大多数水平分支处于第4或第5层，有些向下进入[[白质|白质]]<ref name="Meyer_1987">{{cite journal|title=Forms and spatial arrangement of neurons in the primary motor cortex of man.|first1=G|journal=The Journal of Comparative Neurology|issue=3|doi=10.1002/cne.902620306|year=1987|volume=262|pages=402–28|pmid=3655019|last1=Meyer}}</ref>。

